==Trivia==
*The name "Bellock" is a reference to {{Wp|List of Indiana Jones characters#René Belloq|Belloq}} from ''{{Wp|Raiders of the Lost Ark|Indiana Jones and the Raiders of the Lost Ark}}''.
*The phrase, "You belong in a museum!" is a quote from the character 'Ezreal' of the ''[[wikipedia:League of Legends|League of Legends]]'' franchise, the quote which is itself in reference to a similar quote from ''[[wikipedia:Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade|Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade]]''. <!-- The quote from the movie says: "That belongs in a museum!" / "So do you!" -->
*The crazy archaeologist is the only Wilderness boss which does not drop a pet.

